gstreamer1: gstreamer1 (GStreamer streaming media framework runtime)
gstreamer1:
gstreamer1: GStreamer is a streaming media framework, based on graphs of filters
gstreamer1: which operate on media data. Applications using this library can do
gstreamer1: anything from real-time sound processing to playing videos, and just
gstreamer1: about anything else media-related. Its plugin-based architecture
gstreamer1: means that new data types or processing capabilities can be added
gstreamer1: simply by installing new plugins.
gstreamer1:
gstreamer1: http://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/
gstreamer1: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
